# Build Believe Fit — React frontend environment
# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in. Vite only exposes vars prefixed VITE_.
#
# The anon/publishable key is safe in the client bundle — RLS is the real
# boundary, and privileged admin reads go through the token-gated
# bbf-admin-roster edge function, not the anon key.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://ihclbceghxpuawymlvgi.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# NOTE — the Command Center authorizes SILENTLY. There is no admin token to bundle
# or paste: the data utils send the logged-in admin's session vault_token as
# Authorization: Bearer, and the edge functions + Render verify it server-side and
# check the admin/trainer role (CLAUDE.md §7 — no shared secret in the client). The
# server-side BBF_COACH_AGENT_TOKEN / BBF_ADMIN_TOKEN secrets remain for
# service-to-service callers only.
